{
    "id": "welcome/run-tests",
    "title": "Run the Test Suite",
    "description": "Learn how to run DSPACE's automated tests to ensure your changes are correct.",
    "image": "/assets/quests/run_tests_terminal_dashboard.jpg",
    "npc": "/assets/npc/dChat.jpg",
    "start": "start",
    "dialogue": [
        {
            "id": "start",
            "text": "Testing keeps DSPACE reliable. We'll prep your laptop, run the suite, and log what happened so the next explorer inherits a green build.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "prep",
                    "text": "What do I need?"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "scope",
                    "text": "Which tests are we running?"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "scope",
            "text": "We aim for the same lane as CI: `npm run test:ci` to hit unit and integration checks without browsers. Keep SKIP_E2E=1 for now; if you want extra assurance, add `npm run check` after this flow.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "prep",
                    "text": "Got it, let's gear up."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "prep",
            "text": "Plug in your laptop, sync the repo, and run `nvm use` so Node 20 matches CI. Open the mission logbook so you can note commands, failures, and timestamps.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "install",
                    "text": "Dependencies are installed and workspace is clean.",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "b6fc1ed6-f399-4fdb-9f9d-3913f893f43d",
                            "count": 1
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "70bb8d86-2c4e-4330-9705-371891934686",
                            "count": 1
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "aa82b02f-2617-4474-a91b-29647e4a9780",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "install",
                    "text": "Walk me through the run anyway."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "install",
            "text": "Close stray servers, export SKIP_E2E=1, then run `npm ci` from the repo root. When dependencies settle, clear caches (`rm -rf node_modules/.cache`) if Vitest ever complains.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "run",
                    "text": "Ready to execute tests."
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "run",
                    "text": "I already cleaned up and want to run now.",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "b6fc1ed6-f399-4fdb-9f9d-3913f893f43d",
                            "count": 1
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "70bb8d86-2c4e-4330-9705-371891934686",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "run",
            "text": "Kick off `npm run test:ci` and watch for flake signatures: timeouts, missing Playwright deps, or outdated snapshots. Capture the command, duration, and exit status in the logbook before you rerun anything.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "run-dspace-tests",
                    "text": "Run the suite and record results",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "b6fc1ed6-f399-4fdb-9f9d-3913f893f43d",
                            "count": 1
                        },
                        {
